{
  "info": {
    "name": "MIS Host · Backend",
    "description": "Colección completa de endpoints REST de mis-backend (Spring Boot). Módulos: auth, usuarios, roles, sistemas.\n\n── Niveles de acceso (SecurityConfig) ──\n- [Público]: sin token (auth + actuator health/info).\n- [Colaborador]: cualquier usuario autenticado (admin-sistema, admin-general o supervisor-area). Son las lecturas que alimentan el sidebar/dashboard de cada colaborador.\n- [Admin]: solo rol ADMIN_SISTEMA (gestión de IAM y de sistemas).\n\n── Flujo de autenticación ──\n1. 'Auth > Login' con email/password → devuelve mfaToken (se guarda en {{mfaToken}}).\n2. 'Auth > Verificar OTP' (en dev el OTP fijo es 123456, ver application-dev.yml) → devuelve el JWT (se guarda en {{token}}).\n3. El resto de requests usan Bearer {{token}} automáticamente (heredado de la colección).\n\nVarias peticiones auto-capturan IDs ({{rolId}}, {{sistemaId}}, {{usuarioId}}, {{seccionId}}, {{subseccionId}}, {{moduloId}}) para poder encadenarlas sin copiar/pegar.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "mis-backend-collection"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "mfaToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "usuarioId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "rolId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sistemaId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sistemaSlug", "value": "subsistema-contabilidad", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "seccionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "subseccionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "moduloId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth [Público]",
      "description": "Autenticación con MFA obligatorio (CA-07). Sin token.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (paso 1: credenciales)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@confianza.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "auth", "login" ]
            },
            "description": "password = contraseña en dev, o ID token de Google en prod. Responde MfaChallengeResponse { mfaRequerido, mfaToken, email }. NO emite sesión todavía.\n\nUsuarios semilla de dev (V3__seed_dev.sql):\n- admin@confianza.pe / admin123 (admin-sistema)\n- general@confianza.pe / general123 (admin-general)\n- supervisor@confianza.pe / supervisor123 (supervisor-area)\n\nErrores: 401 credenciales inválidas · 403 usuario desactivado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.mfaToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('mfaToken', body.mfaToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verificar OTP (paso 2: token de sesión)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mfaToken\": \"{{mfaToken}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verificar-otp",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "auth", "verificar-otp" ]
            },
            "description": "En dev el OTP fijo es 123456 (mis.auth.otp.fixed-code). Máx. 5 intentos, un solo uso, TTL 3 min. Responde LoginResponse { token, usuario }.\n\nErrores: 401 OTP incorrecto o desafío expirado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "    if (body.usuario && body.usuario.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('usuarioId', body.usuario.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Colaborador [Autenticado]",
      "description": "Lecturas que puede hacer CUALQUIER usuario autenticado (admin-sistema, admin-general o supervisor-area). Alimentan el sidebar y el dashboard del colaborador. Requieren Bearer {{token}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar sistemas (resumen)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas" ]
            },
            "description": "SistemaResumen[] (contadores agregados, sin árbol). Alimenta sidebar y dashboard."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const arr = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (Array.isArray(arr) && arr.length) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('sistemaId', arr[0].id);",
                  "        if (arr[0].slug) pm.collectionVariables.set('sistemaSlug', arr[0].slug);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener sistema por ID o slug (árbol completo)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaSlug}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaSlug}}" ]
            },
            "description": "{{sistemaSlug}} puede ser el UUID o el slug. Responde el árbol completo Secciones → Subsecciones → Módulos (con icono por sección y módulo, v2.2)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const s = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const sec = (s.secciones || [])[0];",
                  "    if (sec) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('seccionId', sec.id);",
                  "        const sub = (sec.subsecciones || [])[0];",
                  "        if (sub) {",
                  "            pm.collectionVariables.set('subseccionId', sub.id);",
                  "            const mod = (sub.modulos || [])[0];",
                  "            if (mod) pm.collectionVariables.set('moduloId', mod.id);",
                  "        }",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar roles",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles" ]
            },
            "description": "Lista de roles (la consumen los selects del Host)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const arr = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (Array.isArray(arr) && arr.length) pm.collectionVariables.set('rolId', arr[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener rol por ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{rolId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles", "{{rolId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Detalle del rol (RolDto: id, nombre, slug, subsistemas)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Administración · Usuarios [Admin]",
      "description": "Gestión de usuarios. Toda la clase exige rol ADMIN_SISTEMA (Bearer {{token}}).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar usuarios (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/usuarios?page=1&pageSize=20&q=&activo=",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "usuarios" ],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "description": "búsqueda por nombre/email (opcional)" },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "", "description": "true|false (opcional)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "PageResponse<UsuarioDto> { page, pageSize, total, items }."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.items && body.items.length) pm.collectionVariables.set('usuarioId', body.items[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener usuario por ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/usuarios/{{usuarioId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "usuarios", "{{usuarioId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Detalle. 404 si no existe."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"juan.perez@confianza.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"Password.123\",\n  \"rolId\": \"{{rolId}}\",\n  \"subsistemas\": [\"subsistema-contabilidad\", \"subsistema-rrhh\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/usuarios",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "usuarios" ]
            },
            "description": "subsistemas = slugs de sistemas (override individual del rol). Errores: 400 campos requeridos · 409 email duplicado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('usuarioId', body.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"juan.perez@confianza.pe\",\n  \"password\": null,\n  \"rolId\": \"{{rolId}}\",\n  \"subsistemas\": [\"subsistema-contabilidad\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/usuarios/{{usuarioId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "usuarios", "{{usuarioId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza nombre/email/rol/subsistemas. password es opcional (enviar null para no cambiarla)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Cambiar estado (activar/desactivar)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"activo\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/usuarios/{{usuarioId}}/estado",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "usuarios", "{{usuarioId}}", "estado" ]
            },
            "description": "Body { activo: boolean }. Activa/desactiva la cuenta."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Administración · Roles [Admin]",
      "description": "Gestión de roles. GET listar/obtener están en la carpeta Colaborador (autenticados); estos endpoints exigen rol ADMIN_SISTEMA.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Usuarios del rol",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{rolId}}/usuarios",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles", "{{rolId}}", "usuarios" ]
            },
            "description": "UsuarioDto[] vinculados al rol."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Permisos del rol (agrupados por sistema)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{rolId}}/permisos",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles", "{{rolId}}", "permisos" ]
            },
            "description": "PermisoRolSistema[] del rol. Cada item: { rolId, sistemaId, secciones[], subsecciones[], modulos[] } (v2.2)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear rol",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Analista de Crédito\",\n  \"slug\": \"analista-credito\",\n  \"subsistemas\": [\"subsistema-contabilidad\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles" ]
            },
            "description": "slug debe ser kebab-case en minúsculas. subsistemas = slugs habilitados por el rol. Errores: 400 nombre/slug requeridos · 409 slug duplicado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('rolId', body.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar rol",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Analista de Crédito Senior\",\n  \"slug\": \"analista-credito\",\n  \"subsistemas\": [\"subsistema-contabilidad\", \"subsistema-rrhh\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{rolId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles", "{{rolId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "El slug es inmutable tras la creación (se ignora si cambia)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar rol",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{rolId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "roles", "{{rolId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Responde 204 No Content. 409 si el rol tiene usuarios asignados."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Administración · Sistemas [Admin]",
      "description": "Registro de Remotes, estructura y permisos por nivel. GET listar/obtener están en la carpeta Colaborador; estos endpoints exigen rol ADMIN_SISTEMA.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear sistema",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Créditos\",\n  \"slug\": \"subsistema-creditos\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Gestión de créditos\",\n  \"icono\": \"pi pi-credit-card\",\n  \"url\": \"http://localhost:4205/remoteEntry.json\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"estado\": \"inactivo\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas" ]
            },
            "description": "slug = nombre del Remote en federation.manifest.json (kebab-case). estado ∈ activo|mantenimiento|inactivo. Error: 409 slug duplicado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('sistemaId', body.id);",
                  "    if (body.slug) pm.collectionVariables.set('sistemaSlug', body.slug);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar sistema (datos generales)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Créditos\",\n  \"slug\": \"subsistema-creditos\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Gestión integral de créditos\",\n  \"icono\": \"pi pi-credit-card\",\n  \"url\": \"http://localhost:4205/remoteEntry.json\",\n  \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n  \"estado\": \"activo\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza datos generales (la estructura tiene su propio endpoint). El path param es UUID (no admite slug)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar sistema",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Responde 204 No Content. 409 si está asignado a algún rol. Cascada sobre estructura y permisos."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Reemplazar estructura (secciones/subsecciones/módulos)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "[\n  {\n    \"nombre\": \"Operaciones\",\n    \"slug\": \"operaciones\",\n    \"icono\": \"pi pi-folder\",\n    \"subsecciones\": [\n      {\n        \"nombre\": \"Solicitudes\",\n        \"slug\": \"solicitudes\",\n        \"modulos\": [\n          { \"nombre\": \"Nueva solicitud\", \"slug\": \"nueva-solicitud\", \"icono\": \"pi pi-file\", \"activo\": true },\n          { \"nombre\": \"Bandeja\", \"slug\": \"bandeja\", \"icono\": \"pi pi-inbox\", \"activo\": true }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaId}}/estructura",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaId}}", "estructura" ]
            },
            "description": "Reemplaza el árbol completo Secciones → Subsecciones → Módulos. El 'orden' (1-based, v2.1) lo define la posición en el arreglo; 'icono' es opcional por sección/módulo. Depura permisos huérfanos de los 3 niveles en la misma transacción (BE-07)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Permisos del sistema (por rol)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaId}}/permisos",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaId}}", "permisos" ]
            },
            "description": "PermisoRolSistema[] del sistema: por rol, los ids concedidos por nivel { secciones[], subsecciones[], modulos[] } (v2.2)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Guardar permisos de un rol en el sistema (por nivel)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"secciones\": [\"{{seccionId}}\"],\n  \"subsecciones\": [],\n  \"modulos\": [\"{{moduloId}}\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sistemas/{{sistemaId}}/permisos/{{rolId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "sistemas", "{{sistemaId}}", "permisos", "{{rolId}}" ]
            },
            "description": "Upsert de permisos del rol en el sistema POR NIVEL (v2.2), con herencia descendente: conceder un nivel habilita todo lo que cuelga de él. El nivel SISTEMA se administra con el campo 'subsistemas' del rol. Ejecutar antes 'Colaborador > Obtener sistema por ID o slug' para poblar {{seccionId}}/{{moduloId}}."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Utilidad · Actuator [Público]",
      "description": "Endpoints de salud expuestos sin autenticación (management.endpoints).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/actuator/health",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "actuator", "health" ]
            },
            "description": "Estado de la app (liveness/readiness)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Info",
          "request": {
